Package: tidyformula
Title: Build Formulas Using Tidy Selection Helpers
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Damian", "Pavlyshyn", email = "damian.pavlyshyn@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
	       comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6929-878X"))
Description: Provides the function `tidyformula`, which translates formulas containing `tidyselect`-style selection helpers. It expands these helpers by evaluating `dplyr::select` with the relevant selection helper and a supplied data frame.
